  <title><a href="/media-center/newsreleases/2022/finra-promotes-nathaniel-stankard-executive-vice-president-and-chief" hreflang="en">FINRA Promotes Nathaniel Stankard to Executive Vice President and Chief of Staff to the CEO for Regulatory Operations</a></title>
  <link>https://www.finra.org/media-center/newsreleases/2022/finra-promotes-nathaniel-stankard-executive-vice-president-and-chief</link>
  <description>&lt;p&gt;WASHINGTON—FINRA announced today that it has promoted Nathaniel Stankard to Executive Vice President and Chief of Staff to the CEO for Regulatory Operations, effective immediately. In this new role, Stankard will be responsible for providing strategic direction on the integration of FINRA’s regulatory operations, and for helping advance FINRA’s unified approach to regulatory policy.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
